        <h1> Who We Are</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="aboutus-content">
        <p>
            We at Tulsi Foundation believe in the Power of One.
            Founded on 5th August, 2011, Tulsi Foundation is non-profit charitable trust based in Mumbai and Uttarakhand. The main focal areas for the organisation are – Education, Health, Culture and Sports.
            We believe that the freedom to dream, willingness to achieve, and ability to implement empowers a person to transform themselves and the nation. By providing knowledge, holistic development, and cultural awareness to an individual, we are providing them the resources to make an impact.
            We are a team of multi-faceted individuals, striving to bring about a change in our society for a better tomorrow.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>


<div>
